---
// About Section
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-8 section-container-margin">
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Text Section (Left Side) -->
			<div class="bg-white px-6 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-12 md:py-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
				<h2 id="about-heading" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[#BE1C2B] mb-4 md:mb-6" style="color: #BE1C2B;">
					KOZY KOMFORT:
				</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8 text-gray-900">
					We are your trusted Adult Foster Care (AFC) Home in Battle Creek, Michigan!
				</p>
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl leading-loose text-gray-900">
					<p>
						At <strong class="font-bold">Kozy Komfort</strong>, we believe every individual deserves a warm, welcoming environment. 
						Kozy Komfort Assisted Living in Battle Creek, MI, is a licensed adult foster care home providing 
						compassionate, personalized care for up to six seniors. For over 20 years, we've offered a warm, 
						home-like environment where residents receive 24/7 assistance with daily activities such as bathing, 
						dressing, and feeding.
					</p>
					<p>
						Our dedicated caregivers, in partnership with local families, doctors, and agencies, ensure each 
						resident's comfort, safety, and well-being. We provide nutritious home-cooked meals, engaging 
						activities like music and pet therapy, and support for individuals who are aged, physically disabled, 
						or living with Alzheimer's or dementia.
					</p>
					<p class="font-bold text-gray-900">
						Our home is <strong class="font-bold">fully wheelchair accessible</strong>, ensuring all residents can move comfortably 
						and safely throughout the space.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Image Section (Right Side) -->
			<div class="relative h-full min-h-[400px] md:min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden">
				<img
					src="/images/about-section/about-img.jpg"
					alt="Caregiver and resident interaction at Kozy Komfort"
					class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
				/>
				<!-- Gradient fade to blend with background -->
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-white to-transparent"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

